These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, thai
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, pop
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bolivar
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, azure
House: cape-cod, ranch-style
1. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
3. the thai is on the left or right of the russian##3
4. the ranch-style house is not to the right of the cape-cod house##8
5. the russian is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
6. the fan of punk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |
| Nationality    | thai   | russian        |
| Music-Genre   | punk    | pop |
| Cigar     | bolivar  | siglo       |
| Color     | mauve   | azure         |
| House   | ranch-style | cape-cod      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-8-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, jet-ski
There are 2 different favourite colors: black, aquamarine
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, fonseca
There 2 different types of food: avocado, kiwi
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, manager
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the fonseca-smoker is not to the right of the person eating kiwi##8
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Transport         | tram   | jet-ski |
| Color   | aquamarine  | black     |
| Cigar   | prince  | fonseca        |
| Food           | avocado     | kiwi       |
| Job         | mechanic | manager     |

