There are 2 different favourite colors: emerald, blood-red
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, july
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
2. the person who likes emerald is not to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##8
3. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
4. the person who's birthday is in november is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |
