The people have 2 different jobs:  dressmaker, engineer
1. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##8
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
3. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
4. the engineer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Movie-Genre          | crime      | sports     |
| Game         | monopoly     | whist |
| Sport   | swimming | biathlon       |
| Transport   | bike    | snowmobile    |
| Job           | dressmaker        | engineer    |

