3. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Birthday          | may     | december |
| City           | paris | edinburgh |
| Transport   | taxi     | quad-bike   |
| Sport   | surfing     | skateboarding    |
